OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, this most
OL,7,Fpersistent across the north and west.
OL,8,
OL,9,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,10,Fwith outbreaks of rain, occasionally
OL,11,Fheavy in the west. Then staying cloudy
OL,12,Fovernight with patchy rain and
OL,13,Fdrizzle, this mostly in the west.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FMainly cloudy with outbreaks
OL,16,Fof mostly light rain in the morning.
OL,17,FBecoming largely dry in the afternoon
OL,18,Falthough some drizzle in the
OL,19,Fnorthwest. Some brightness around the
OL,20,FMoray Firth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
