OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fin west on Wednesday with early
OL,7,Fdrizzle, dry bright and very warm in
OL,8,Feast. Mainly dry, bright and very warm
OL,9,Fon Thursday and Friday. Rain in far
OL,10,Fnorthwest Friday.
